
'''Dorothée Munyaneza''' (wavutse 1982) ni umuririmbyi, umukinnyi wa filime, umubyinnyi wo mu [[bwongereza]]  ukomoka mu [[Rwanda]]. Yagaragaye mu bice bibiri bya filimi, ''Samedi Détente'' na ''Unwanted'', byombi bijyanye na [[Itsembabwoko ry’u Rwanda ry’1994|jenoside yakorewe abatutsi]] mu Rwanda muri 1994<ref name="NYT" />.

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Munyaneza yavukiye i [[Kigali]], mu [[Rwanda]]. <ref name="NYT">https://www.nytimes.com/2017/09/19/arts/dance/dorothee-munyaneza-unwanted-rwanda.html</ref> Se ni umuvugabutumwa, naho nyina ni umunyamakuru. <ref name="Provence">https://www.laprovence.com/article/sorties-loisirs/4498002/la-resiliente.html</ref> Munyaneza n'umuryango we bavuye i Kigali mu gihe cya jenoside yakorewe abatutsi mu [[Itsembabwoko ry’u Rwanda ry’1994|Rwanda]], igihe Munyaneza yari afite imyaka 12. <ref name="NYT" /> Nyina yakoraga mu muryango utegamiye kuri Leta, bityo akaba yarashoboye kurinda umuryango we, ndetse abona inzira ijyera i Londres mu [[Ubwongereza|Bwongereza]]. <ref name="Provence" /> <ref name="CR">https://www.chicagoreader.com/chicago/unwanted-dorothee-munyaneza/Content?oid=58806676</ref> <ref name="Liberation">https://next.liberation.fr/theatre/2015/01/19/dorothee-munyaneza-une-danseuse-de-haut-volt_1184051</ref> Munyaneza yize muri Lycée Français Charles de Gaulle . Mu gihe yigaga yahuye na Christine Sigwart washinze Jonas Foundation, umuryango utabara imbabare ugamije guhuza abana babimukira n'imiryango yabo. akunda umuziki, kuko yize umuziki muri Jonas Foundation. <ref name="Provence" /> <ref name="Point">http://www.lepoint.fr/culture/dorothee-munyaneza-choregraphe-chanteuse-et-rescapee-du-genocide-du-rwanda-07-07-2017-2141275_3.php#xtmc=dorothee-munyaneza&xtnp=1&xtcr=1</ref> Munyaneza yize umuziki n'ubumenyi mbonezamubano muri kaminuza ya Canterbury Christ . <ref name="CB">https://www.culturebot.org/2017/09/27508/refusing-to-bow-down-dorothee-munyaneza-speaks-about-unwanted/</ref> Ubu atuye i Marseille, mu [[Ubufaransa|Bufaransa]], <ref name="Provence" /> <ref name="CB" /> kandi afite umwana w'umukobwa. <ref name="Liberation" />

== Umwuga ==
Munyaneza yatewe inkunga no gukora ku ngingo ya jenoside yakorewe abatutsi mu Rwanda muri 1994 nyuma yo kubona ibyegeranyo kuri iyo ngingo, cyane cyane iyanditswe na Thierry Michel ivuga ku bikorwa bya Denis Mukwege . <ref name="FC">http://frenchculture.org/performing-arts/6181-dorothee-munyaneza-about-unwanted</ref>

Munyaneza niwe wakoze  amajwi ya firime ya ''[[Hotel Rwanda]]'' . Yatangiye ari umuririmbyi n'umwanditsi w'inkuru muri firime, ariko nyuma atangira kubyina muburyo busa nuburyo yabyinnye akiri umwana mu [[Rwanda]].  Yakoranye na François Verret [ fr ], Robyn Orlin, Rachid Ouramdane [ fr ], Nan Goldin, Mark Tompkins, Ko Murobushi na Alain Buffard [ fr ] <ref name="NYT" />  <ref name="RFI">http://www.rfi.fr/emission/20161106-dorothee-munyaneza-rediffusion</ref> Nkumuririmbyi, yashyize ahagaragara alubumu ye ya mbere wenyine muri 2010, yakozwe na Martin Russell .   Muri 2012, yakoranye n'umwongereza James Seymour Brett gukora alubumu ''Earth Songs'' . <ref name="CB" /> <ref name="BAC" /> Muri 2013, yagaragaye mu gitaramo cya Rachid Ouramdane i Rennes, mu Bufaransa. Mu gitaramo, yavuze amazina y'Abanyalijeriya bishwe mu bwicanyi bwabereye i Paris mu 1961 . <ref name="Liberation" />

Muri 2014, Munyaneza yakoze filimi ''Samedi Détente'' (kuruhuka kuwagatandatu). Yibanze kuri jenoside yakorewe abatutsi mu [[Rwanda]], uburyo abantu 1000000 bapfuye mu minsi 100, <ref>https://www.nytimes.com/2016/01/16/theater/review-samedi-detente-looks-back-at-the-horrors-of-rwanda.html?_r=0&module=inline</ref> n'ubunararibonye bwe kuri jenoside. <ref name="FT">https://www.ft.com/content/28e90f9a-de86-11e7-a0d4-0944c5f49e46</ref> Igikorwa cyatangiriye i Nîmes, mu [[Bufaransa]]. <ref>https://culturebox.francetvinfo.fr/theatre/samedi-detente-une-piece-de-dorothee-munyaneza-pour-dire-le-genocide-rwandais-255527</ref>

Muri 2017, yakoze ''Unwanted'', filimi ye ya kabiri ijyanye na jenoside yakorewe abatutsi mu [[Rwanda]].  Igikorwa cyagaragayemo Alain Mahé  <ref name="NYT" />    ''Unwanted'' ifite intego yibanze kubagore bafashwe kungufu nabana babo batwite.  Munyaneza yerekanye ''Unwanted'' mu iserukiramuco rya d'Avignon 2017, <ref name="Monde">https://www.lemonde.fr/afrique/article/2017/03/29/de-paris-a-kigali-l-art-fait-le-printemps_5102760_3212.html#zFI1V0CjwKwcGUCd.99</ref> <ref name="RFI2">http://www.rfi.fr/emission/20170709-festival-avignon-2017-unwanted-dorothee-munyaneza</ref> <ref name="Liberation2">https://next.liberation.fr/theatre/2017/07/13/dorothee-munyaneza-au-choeur-des-tenebres_1583699</ref> ndetse no muri Festival d'automne à Paris [ fr ] <ref name="FT" />

